 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Drinkware, bags, tech — the full event SWAG range.</p>
 </a>
 <a href="/custom-yeti-drinkware-las-vegas/" class="group rounded-xl border border-navy-700/40 bg-navy-900/40 p-6 transition-all hover:border-gold-500/40 hover:bg-navy-900/60">
 <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-white group-hover:text-gold-400">Custom Yeti Drinkware</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Higher-tier giveaway for qualified leads or sponsor gifting.</p>
 </a>
 </div>
 </div>
 </section>

 <section class="bg-navy-900/60 py-20">
 <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
 <h2 class="mb-4 font-heading text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Ready to brand your lanyards?</h2>
 <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-gray-300">Send your art, quantity, and event date.</p>
 <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
 <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex min-h-[48px] items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-gold-500 px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-navy-950 transition-all hover:bg-gold-400">Get a Free Quote</a>
 <a href="tel:+17029048923" class="inline-flex min-h-[48px] items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-600 px-8 py-4 font-mono text-base font-medium text-white transition-all hover:border-gold-500 hover:text-gold-500">702.904.8923</a>
 </div>
 </div>
 </section>
</BaseLayout>
